o; Dual: Svelte, Vite, Nuxt; Faux: Remix, Gatsby; CommonJS: Next.js&quot; width=&quot;1000&quot; height=&quot;562&quot; srcset=&quot;https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/5S0fXVH_9Q-600.jpeg 600w, https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/5S0fXVH_9Q-1000.jpeg 1000w&quot; sizes=&quot;(min-width: 106.25em) 82.75em, (min-width: 61.25em) calc(91.43vw - 13.25em), 100vw&quot;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&quot;image/avif&quot; srcset=&quot;https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/AKCZ2Ya84_-600.avif 600w, https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/AKCZ2Ya84_-1000.avif 1000w&quot; sizes=&quot;(min-width: 106.25em) 82.75em, (min-width: 61.25em) calc(91.43vw - 13.25em), 100vw&quot;&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; src=&quot;https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/AKCZ2Ya84_-600.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;ESM support was stable in Node 12+ and 11ty added it for Node 18+ so we’re a *little* late here.&quot; width=&quot;1000&quot; height=&quot;562&quot; srcset=&quot;https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/AKCZ2Ya84_-600.jpeg 600w, https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/AKCZ2Ya84_-1000.jpeg 1000w&quot; sizes=&quot;(min-width: 106.25em) 82.75em, (min-width: 61.25em) calc(91.43vw - 13.25em), 100vw&quot;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&quot;image/avif&quot; srcset=&quot;https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/WDJiv3YOHn-600.avif 600w, https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/WDJiv3YOHn-1000.avif 1000w&quot; sizes=&quot;(min-width: 106.25em) 82.75em, (min-width: 61.25em) calc(91.43vw - 13.25em), 100vw&quot;&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; src=&quot;https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/WDJiv3YOHn-600.jpeg&quot; alt=&quot;11ty is written in ESM, adds support for ESM in your projects, but ESM remains optional.&quot; width=&quot;1000&quot; height=&quot;562&quot; srcset=&quot;https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/WDJiv3YOHn-600.jpeg 600w, https://www.zachleat.com/img/built/WDJiv3YOHn-1000.jpeg 1000w&quot; sizes=&quot;(min-width: 106.25em) 82.75em,