    <title>Eleventy v3.0.0 is now available!</title>
    <link href="https://www.zachleat.com/web/eleventy-v3/" />
    <updated>2024-10-02T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <id>https://www.zachleat.com/web/eleventy-v3/</id>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;After over a year of work, our very first stable release of ESM-friendly 3.0 is now available: &lt;strong&gt;Eleventy v3.0.0&lt;/strong&gt; 🎈🐀&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are very excited to see this ship and look forward to what y’all build with it 🏆&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/11ty/eleventy/releases/tag/v3.0.0&quot;&gt;Eleventy v3.0.0: Possums ❤️ ESM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (includes full release notes, features, upgrade guide, and thank you notes!)&lt;/p&gt;
